- SESSION_CONTEXT.md - Complete development session context and current state
- docs/IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md - 8-week implementation roadmap
- src/lib/mcp/README.md - MCP protocol layer documentation
- src/lib/data/README.md - Mock data layer documentation

