## Important Notes
- Use TypeScript strict mode throughout
- Follow MCP 0.1.0 specification exactly
- All write operations restricted to organization ID 100048 (ACME)
- Use cursor-based pagination (max 25 per page)
- Dual response format: JSON + human-readable guidance
- Include tool annotations: readOnlyHint, destructiveHint, idempotentHint, openWorldHint

## Dependencies
Core: next@14, react@18, jsonwebtoken, uuid, zod, @faker-js/faker
Dev: typescript, vitest, playwright, eslint, tailwindcss

## Testing
- Unit tests in tests/unit/ using Vitest
- Integration tests in tests/integration/
- E2E tests in tests/e2e/ using Playwright
- Target: >80% code coverage

## Deployment
- Platform: Vercel
- Environment: Production + Development
- Config: vercel.json with rewrites and CORS headers
